  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CharacterExtractor
    Interface for extracting individual characters along with their bounding boxes from a file.
    DocumentSegmenter
    Building hierarchical geometric structure containing: pages, zones, lines, words and characters.
    ReadingOrderResolver
    Determining the order in which the elements on all levels should be read.
    ZoneClassifier
    Interface for classifying zones of the document.
